    &quot;Well it looks like you got your first rider of the day.&quot;<br>
~She smirked a bit, then smiled again at Nefertiti~<br>
    &quot;I should get back to work on Hercules, I hope you have fun Nef.&quot;<br>
~Turning on her heel, she walked back to the center of the pasture and starts working with the horses again. She closed her eyes and called out to the stallion this time, commanding the mares to stay where they were. Slowly, but surely, after much proding, Hercules walked up to her and nudged her side. She opened her eyes and rewarded him with a carrot. She ten called a few of the mares over, and to her surprize, he didn't even glance at them. Letting one of her rare, hundred watt smiles play at her lips, she patted his neck and let him go back to grazing.~ <p>            ~Robin~
